3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the development of a semantic segmentation module for autonomous driving, which is an application of AI. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper discusses the development of a semantic segmentation module for autonomous driving, which is a robotics application.
